divs: Sighting DetailsMy brother called and invited me and my son to go to the lake (South Holston)that afternoon. It was a gorgeous day. I was trying to mow the yard and had given up cause my mower was not pulling. Anyway we went to the lake. I usually take my camera. I don't know anything about photography. My camera is a kodak easy share point and shoot. 5 megapixels. I didn't even realize that this might be a ufo until I got home and downloaded the photos to the computer. My wife said it is a cloud, but the sky was a beautiful blue with no clouds. And it is probably some sort of light reflection or something. But I have taken about a 1000 pictures up on the lake over the last several years and have never had anything ever show up on it. Anyway make of it what you will. It very will may be some photgraphic boo boo. We didn't hear any sounds or anything.
